12
00:02:13,299 --> 00:02:16,219
PROFESSOR X:  Are we
destined down this path?

13
00:02:16,594 --> 00:02:21,766
 Destined to destroy ourselves
like so many species before us?

14
00:02:23,893 --> 00:02:25,311
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

15
00:02:25,394 --> 00:02:29,148
 Or can we evolve fast
enough to change ourselves?

16
00:02:29,774 --> 00:02:31,150
 Change our fate?

17
00:02:32,151 --> 00:02:34,403
(DISTANT GROWLING)

18
00:02:37,365 --> 00:02:40,743
 Is the future truly set?

19
