22
00:04:10,207 --> 00:04:11,250
They're here!

23
00:04:15,838 --> 00:04:16,881
(PANTING)

24
00:04:16,964 --> 00:04:17,965
Time's up.

25
00:04:18,049 --> 00:04:19,091
WARPATH: Sentinels!

26
00:04:23,346 --> 00:04:24,347
Sunspot!

27
00:04:29,268 --> 00:04:30,394
KITTY: Let's go.

28
